channel.title: In Wilderness Image Not Showing [PICS]
channel.description:
I am using Project Insanity as a base. I decided to switch from Project Insanity's default client to this client because it looks much nicer.
[url=http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/downloads/268520-v2-new-many-features-ref-pi-client.html]http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/downloads/268520-v2-new-many-features-ref-pi-client.html[/url]
Now when I go into my wilderness area it does not show that I am in the wilderness.
What it should show: [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/t63xpv.png[/img]
MSN: [email]austinrouse@hotmail.com[/email]
*Yes I added the sprites to the new client
